   </teiHeader> <facsimile> <graphic url="HS_AM23366Ba"/> <graphic url="HS_AM23366Ba_R"/> </facsimile> <text type="letter-card"> <body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="https://www.theatermuseum.at/de/object/243dddfcfa/"/>Herrn Hermann Bahr</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb165" type="place">Wien Ob. St. Veit</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb220" type="place">Veitli<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>enga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e.</rs></addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="https://www.theatermuseum.at/de/object/243dddfcfa/"/><date>17. 8.</date></dateline></opener><p><salute>lieber Hermann, </salute><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2173" subtype="implied">wir</rs> wollen Freitag um 8 in dem <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL072-1"/><rs ref="#pmb304" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Kuffner</hi> Garten</rs><note type="commentary" xml:id="KL072-1h">Gastgarten des <rs ref="#pmb304" type="place">Ottakringer Bräu</rs>. Das Lokal gehörte zu der im 16. <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>er Gemeindebezirk (<rs ref="#pmb66" type="place">Ottakring</rs>) angesiedelten Brauerei <rs ref="#pmb6" type="place">Kuffner</rs>.</note> in <rs ref="#pmb63" type="place">Hietzing</rs> nachtmahlen; – und hoffen<tei:space unit="chars" quantity="1"></tei:space><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr, wenn du nichts anderes vorha<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t, dich dort zu treffen.</p><p>Zieh<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t du ein andres Rendezvous vor, so ver<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tändige mich.</p><closer>Von Herzen<lb/>dein <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div></body> </text></TEI>